  "worklog": "# brainTrade Work Log\n*Check this anytime to see what I'm doing and how I'm thinking.*\n\n## 2026-05-04 19:22 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 1] BTC net fades, SOL zero longs, cross-asset defensive\n\n**Task:** Run fresh P1 copy intelligence after P4 showed fast RANGE but slow TREND/STOP persisted, checking whether BTC/ETH improvement holds and whether SOL/HYPE shorts soften.\n\n**Finding:**\n- Both bots are alive (`pm-bot`, `hl-bot`).\n- Rotation pointed to **P1**.\n- Ran `/home/ubuntu/clawd/scripts/copy-intel-tracker.py`: **BTC 5L/4S**, **ETH 3L/4S**, **SOL 0L/8S**.\n- Current top-book notional: BTC **+$20.83M net long**, ETH **-$15.14M net short**, SOL **-$5.91M net short**, HYPE **-$9.57M net short**.\n- BTC net faded **+$22.61M \u2192 +$20.83M**, now below the +21M watch level, and breadth deteriorated **6L/3S \u2192 5L/4S**.\n- `anon-0xecb6` BTC LONG trimmed **$18.72M \u2192 $17.96M**; `anon-0xfc66` trimmed **$4.43M \u2192 $4.24M**; `anon-0x57dd` trimmed **$3.38M \u2192 $3.06M**.\n- `beatmaker1` BTC LONG nearly vanished **$495K \u2192 $33K**.\n- `anon-0x8fcc` remains BTC SHORT **$4.13M**; `anon-0x3bca` reduced BTC SHORT **$496K \u2192 $289K**.\n- Cross-asset picture deteriorated: ETH worsened to **-$15.14M** and breadth slipped **3L/4S**, SOL is now **0L/8S** with **no top-trader longs** and **-$5.91M** net short, and HYPE remains **-$9.57M**. `ecb6` remains hedged: BTC LONG **$17.96M** vs ETH SHORT **$14.45M**, SOL SHORT **$4.88M**, HYPE SHORT **$1.88M**.\n- I wrote the artifact to `/home/ubuntu/clawd/research/p1-btc-net-fades-sol-zero-longs-crossasset-defensive-2026-05-04-1922.md`.\n\n**My thinking:** BTC is still net-long, but the last BTC/ETH improvement is fading and SOL is now unanimously short among tracked traders. This is clearly BTC relative-strength with alt defensive hedging, not broad risk-on. P4's slow TREND/STOP block remains justified.\n\n**Decision:** Downgrade P1 to **BTC bullish but fading / alt defensive**. Keep `8fcc` on BTC conflict wat